data.name: ReportExportGET_ReportParametersText
data.value:
Suggest to use report FlexCommonTasks.flxr/MultiValue DataBound Parameters as example.
The report parameters, please see the response of action parameters. e.g:

If the parameter is multi-value, please set the parameters for many times, e.g:
parameters.pCategory=1&parameters.pCustomers=3&...
